description: Welcome to Port 45, South Boston’s Premier Luxury Building, situated in one of the most desirable neighborhoods of Southie. This beautiful penthouse 2-bed 2-bath + den/study unit offers a serene garden view and a unique layout that combines luxury and functionality. Step onto your private outdoor balcony or head upstairs to your additional private roof deck, complete with built in hot and cold water connections and a gas fire pit and grille. Each bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. The modern kitchen is equipped with quartz counters, stainless appliances, large island, flowing into the living/dining area with access to your private balcony. Port 45, provides an array of amenities to residents including a common roof deck with panoramic views, concierge services, a grand lobby common area, fitness center, club room, elevated courtyard, pet spa, garage with access to charging stations, to only name a few! Located just a few blocks from the Seaport.
